                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1" defective="false">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; the name of the archbishop Qerǝllos and of the bishop Ṗeṭros; the name of the donor (?) and other individuals.&#xD;
A few lines (2 or 4) on the incipit page of Texts I, II, and IV (alternating with black lines for Texts I and IV); two lines of the incipit of Texts III and V; initial lines of some sections in Text I and of some paragraphs in Text IV; some words in “Tǝmḫǝrtä ḫǝbuʾat” (Text II); directives for the ministers; titles of Biblical books; words: ʾardǝʾǝt in Text I, ʾab, dǝngǝl and eṗṗes qoṗṗosat in Text IV. Abbreviations; some notes in the margins; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
